data.description: Well taken care of bloomfield home two story house is located in a quiet& family-friendly neighborhood in Oak Point. Upon entering the house, you are greeted by a spacious & open living room, which has large windows that allow plenty of natural light to come in. The living room features high ceilings, neutral walls,& durable wood floors, which extends throughout the house. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with sleek granite countertops, ss appliances, ample cabinet space,& a convenient center island, perfect for culinary enthusiasts &casual diners alike. Four well-appointed bedrooms offer peaceful sanctuaries for rest& relaxation. The master suite is a true retreat, featuring an ensuite bath with vanity, a soaking tub,&separate shower. The outdoor space is a haven of tranquility, offering a covered patio& a sprawling green lawn, providing ample room for gardening &outdoor activities. Don't miss the opportunity to make 908 Longhorn Drive your forever home!
